### to force an error set to force-error 
Get http://localhost:3000/users/force-error
Authorization: Bearer <Bearer token>

### Redact test - with Authorization token
GET http://localhost:3000/logger-redact-test
Authorization: Bearer test-secret-token-123

### Redact test - without Authorization token
GET http://localhost:3000/logger-redact-test

### Sentry test route
GET http://localhost:3000/boom

### Sentry direct ping (returns eventId)
GET http://localhost:3000/sentry-ping
